flowchart LR
    A[User Inputs Resume + Goals] --> B[Resume Parser + Normalizer]
    C[Job Sources + User Saved Jobs] --> D[Job Ingest + Structuring]

    B --> E[Profile Vector Store]
    D --> F[Role Requirement Store]

    E --> G[Fit Scoring Engine]
    F --> G

    G --> H[Gap Analysis + Priority Actions]
    G --> I[Referral Discovery Module]

    H --> J[Outreach Prompt Builder]
    I --> J

    J --> K[LLM Outreach Generation]
    K --> L[User Review + Edit + Send]

    L --> M[Outcome Capture: reply, interview, conversion]
    M --> N[Learning Loop: prompt tuning + ranking updates]
    N --> G
    N --> J

    O[Instrumentation Layer] --> B
    O --> D
    O --> G
    O --> L
    O --> M
